{"tid":1447393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉貼] 流傳清息指若示威者殺死由公安冒充的警察 警隊將安排香港警察交換身份","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:14.000Z","uid":35639,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"772377555169d4b2d44164e0beda83891b4eda99","tid":1447393,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2938827949492653?s=1044711040&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F197517173623758%2Fposts%2F2938827949492653%3Fs%3D1044711040%26sfns%3Dmo&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTLktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=1918c0cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2938827949492653?s=1044711040&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n轉自雲海facebook<br />\n啱啱收到一啲警隊嘅內部通訊，表示香港警察高層42樓安排左一個緊急情況，萬一有示威者打死左冒充香港警察嘅大陸公安，警隊裏面將會整死一個警員互換身份交差！當然冇辦法知道訊息真實性,(fact check 唔到，sorly）若果係真嘅話，你哋警察都人人自危啦，講真唔使示威者殺左一個公安先啦，警隊自己殺死幾個同袍屈示威又得啫！警嫂你放心玩啦，玩完你老公都死撚埋無人追硏你！<br />\n<br />\n如消息屬實<br />\n本人強烈抗議香港政府罔顧警察性命<br />\n支持香港警察揪出內鬼 以防被祭旗<br />\n祝福好人一生平安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee01c260c7ef0e0a3214f07a0f96247530817cb","tid":1447393,"uid":35639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607dc9dcc9068f04b65369700f6c6e0e7f6008ca","tid":1447393,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"aa8005dbcaa0e1dda843cab2c4528b3da4c6b119","tid":1447393,"uid":35639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b79d877e28aeebb6eef8c374349ce0ef7ed9bd","tid":1447393